# Multi-PDF RAG Assistant

A Streamlit-based GenAI application that allows users to upload one or more PDF documents, ask natural language questions, and receive answers grounded only in the uploaded content.

## Features
- Multi-PDF upload
- Semantic search using Sentence Transformers
- FAISS vector retrieval
- OpenAI-based answer generation
- Page-level source citations
- Document summarization
- Cached indexing for faster reuse

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Streamlit
- Sentence Transformers
- FAISS
- OpenAI API
- PyPDF
